<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Intel Sustainability Timeline</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>

<header class="hero">
    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/c9/Intel-logo.svg"
    alt="Intel Logo" class="logo">

    <h1>Sustainability Through the Ages</h1>
    <p>
        Discover Intel's journey toward creating a more sustainable future
        through innovation and responsible technology.
    </p>
</header>

<section class="timeline">

<div class="card">
    <h2>2020</h2>
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497436072909-f5e4be0d1e4"
    alt="Solar energy">

    <h3>Renewable Energy Expansion</h3>

    <div class="details">
        Intel increased investment in renewable energy sources to reduce environmental impact.
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2>2022</h2>
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518770660439-4636190af475"
    alt="Technology">

    <h3>Water Conservation Goals</h3>

    <div class="details">
        Intel focused on reducing water use and restoring local water ecosystems.
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2>2025</h2>
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1473341304170-971dccb5ac1d"
    alt="Green city">

    <h3>Green Manufacturing</h3>

    <div class="details">
        Manufacturing processes became more energy efficient and environmentally conscious.
    </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2>2030</h2>
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494526585095-c41746248156"
    alt="Future technology">

    <h3>Net Positive Impact</h3>

    <div class="details">
        Intel aims to create a positive environmental footprint through innovation.
    </div>
</div>

</section>

<footer>
    Scroll through the timeline | Hover over cards to learn more
</footer>

</body>
</html>
